com.simiacryptus.mindseye.layers.cudnn

Class PoolingLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.NNLayer
      • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.layers.cudnn.PoolingLayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LayerPrecision<PoolingLayer>, Serializable

    public class PoolingLayer
extends NNLayer
implements LayerPrecision<PoolingLayer>
    The standard image-pixel pooling layer. Using a configurable stride and window size, reduces pixels using either the Max or Avg operation.
